{"parse":{"title":"Wladimir Tchertkoff","pageid":11647625,"revid":808620184,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:222px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Devant_OMS_1.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/18/Devant_OMS_1.jpg/220px-Devant_OMS_1.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"176\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/18/Devant_OMS_1.jpg/330px-Devant_OMS_1.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/18/Devant_OMS_1.jpg/440px-Devant_OMS_1.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"3000\" data-file-height=\"2400\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Devant_OMS_1.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Wladimir Tchertkoff in front of the <a href=\"/wiki/WHO\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"WHO\">WHO</a> building, asking for a modification of the WHO-IAEA agreement, 26 April 2007</div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:222px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:20110426-IWHO-15-WTchertkoff-d.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5b/20110426-IWHO-15-WTchertkoff-d.jpg/220px-20110426-IWHO-15-WTchertkoff-d.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"323\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5b/20110426-IWHO-15-WTchertkoff-d.jpg/330px-20110426-IWHO-15-WTchertkoff-d.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5b/20110426-IWHO-15-WTchertkoff-d.jpg/440px-20110426-IWHO-15-WTchertkoff-d.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"770\" data-file-height=\"1132\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:20110426-IWHO-15-WTchertkoff-d.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>26 Avril 2011</div></div></div>\n<p><b>Wladimir Tchertkoff</b> is an <a href=\"/wiki/Italy\" title=\"Italy\">Italian</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Journalist\" title=\"Journalist\">journalist</a>.\n</p><p>He released with Emanuela Andreoli in 2003 the film <i>The Sacrifice</i>, a documentary on the <a href=\"/wiki/Chernobyl_liquidators\" title=\"Chernobyl liquidators\">liquidators</a> of the <a href=\"/wiki/Chernobyl\" title=\"Chernobyl\">Chernobyl</a> nuclear power plant. This film received an award from the <a href=\"/wiki/%C3%8Ele-de-France_(region)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"\u00cele-de-France (region)\">\u00cele-de-France</a> council for the best scientific and environment documentary in November 2004.\n</p><p>He has also received the award of the best documentary of the Festival of Scientific Movies of <a href=\"/wiki/Oullins\" title=\"Oullins\">Oullins</a>, France.\n</p><p>Tchertkoff is the author of <i>Le Crime de Tchernobyl, le Goulag nucl\u00e9aire</i> (<i>The Crime of Chernobyl, the Nuclear Goulag</i>) published by Actes Sud, Paris.\n</p><p>He is also one of the founders of the organisation <i>Children of Chernobyl Belarus</i>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Filmography\">Filmography</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Wladimir_Tchertkoff&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Filmography\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><span class=\"languageicon\">(in French)</span> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.dissident-media.org/fichier_real/piege_atomique.ram\"><i>The Atomic Trap</i> (<i>Le Pi\u00e8ge atomique</i>) <small>(see online)</small></a>. 47 mn Documentary (1998).</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Bibliography\">Bibliography</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Wladimir_Tchertkoff&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Bibliography\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><span class=\"languageicon\">(in French)</span> Wladimir Tchertkoff, <i>Le Crime de Tchernobyl, le Goulag nucl\u00e9aire</i>, Actes Sud, April 2006 <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/2-7427-6042-3\" title=\"Special:BookSources/2-7427-6042-3\">2-7427-6042-3</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Wladimir_Tchertkoff&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><span class=\"languageicon\">(in French)</span> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.dissident-media.org/infonucleaire/sacrifice.html\">The Sacrifice</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"languageicon\">(in French)</span> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://enfantsdetchernobylbelarus.doubleclic.asso.fr/\">Children of Chernobyl Belarus</a></li></ul>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n</p>\n<div role=\"navigation\" class=\"navbox\" aria-labelledby=\"Authority_control_frameless_&amp;#124;text-top_&amp;#124;10px_&amp;#124;alt=Edit_this_at_Wikidata_&amp;#124;link=https&amp;#58;//www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q3569552&amp;#124;Edit_this_at_Wikidata\" style=\"padding:3px\"><table class=\"nowraplinks hlist navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;color:inherit\"><tbody><tr><th id=\"Authority_control_frameless_&amp;#124;text-top_&amp;#124;10px_&amp;#124;alt=Edit_this_at_Wikidata_&amp;#124;link=https&amp;#58;//www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q3569552&amp;#124;Edit_this_at_Wikidata\" scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\"><a href=\"/wiki/Help:Authority_control\" title=\"Help:Authority control\">Authority control</a> <a href=\"https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q3569552\" title=\"Edit this at Wikidata\"><img alt=\"Edit 